{"tid":348300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★馬時亨：強調「港鐵只是提供多一個選擇」，「不是一定要搭港鐵」。","createTime":"2017-08-05T14:48:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T11:50:20.000Z","uid":19454,"like":50,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d714e69b4f26d24f759c4eebc62c551bf47d2055","tid":348300,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T14:48:50.000Z","msg":"港鐵指，觀塘線延線至下午4時已經接載約10萬人次乘客，主席馬時亨下午三時左右到何文田站視察，感謝市民支持。他稱新線投入服務初期，出現輕微「甩漏」，希望市民明白新車站服務需時磨合，並就此向市民致歉。對於有愛民邨居民指何文田站和區內屋邨距離較遠，他承認車站和愛民邨距離遠，明白市民可能寧願繼續選搭巴士或小巴，<span style=\"color: red;\">強調「港鐵只是提供多一個選擇」，又謂市民可按自己需要安排，「不是一定要搭港鐵」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/港聞/50092/-觀塘延線通車-居民嫌車站遠-馬時亨-不一定要搭港鐵\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2F50092%2F-%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E5%BB%B6%E7%B7%9A%E9%80%9A%E8%BB%8A-%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E5%AB%8C%E8%BB%8A%E7%AB%99%E9%81%A0-%E9%A6%AC%E6%99%82%E4%BA%A8-%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E8%A6%81%E6%90%AD%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5&d=eS%2Bb0lPdHDcqu4i69VXaAUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=0318ba92\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/港聞/50092/-觀塘延線通車-居民嫌車站遠-馬時亨-不一定要搭港鐵</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d228b87d3060aa41b34792f01d84d060d9d69e","tid":348300,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T14:49:28.000Z","msg":"不是一定要搭港鐵」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25a3209d367e1eee0ed443fa80f62dfdb989234","tid":348300,"uid":55597,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T14:50:57.000Z","msg":"咁高鐵都唔撚一定要搭啦<br />\n一乜撚野地兩檢，收皮啦"},{"pid":"3d9755daf52a83433341bd0468d3755f65e9ec27","tid":348300,"uid":114097,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T14:5